author: Matt Ellentuck
title: Rob Gronkowski tried his hardest to get someone to say '69' at the 2017 Daytona 500
text:
Nice?
Rob Gronkowski loves the number 69.
He tried to get this woman to say the number on TV at the Daytona 500 and really led her to the finish line. But the whole joke just went right past her.
Gronk gives monster girl obvious clue about speed limit, but she misses it pic.twitter.com/MAJ40c7bTJ 
— CJ Fogler (@cjzero) February 26, 2017 I’m not sure how much more obvious he could’ve been here.
He asked her what her favorite speed limit was. That’s a weird question. He asked if it was around 70. That was the real hint. And, well, he’s Gronk; the same guy who missed a free throw in high school to keep the score at 69 .
But we appreciate her answer nonetheless, because cars going as fast as possible is what makes racing fun.
Still, Nice!
